    <item>
      <title>印度高温现在比降雨更能预测食品价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/india-s-heat-is-now-a-better-predictor-of-food-prices-than-rain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰控股有限公司表示，追踪气温上升趋势正成为预测印度食品通胀的更好方法，比经济学家通常依赖的降雨模式更准确。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/india-s-heat-is-now-a-better-predictor-of-food-prices-than-rain</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 09:10:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>凉鞋需求强劲，Birkenstock 确认前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/birkenstock-affirms-outlook-amid-strong-demand-for-sandals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Birkenstock Holding Plc 确认了其 2024 年财务目标，并报告了强劲的盈利增长，因为消费者抢购更多高端凉鞋和木屐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/birkenstock-affirms-outlook-amid-strong-demand-for-sandals</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 09:10:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>董事会考虑发行红股后，信实股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/ambani-s-reliance-to-consider-one-on-one-bonus-share-issue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[信实工业有限公司 (Reliance Industries Ltd.) 表示，将考虑发行红股——这是该公司七年来的首次——其亿万富翁董事长穆克什·安巴尼 (Mukesh Ambani) 希望在继续向面向消费者的业务多元化发展的同时，奖励小股东。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/ambani-s-reliance-to-consider-one-on-one-bonus-share-issue</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 08:26:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市因降息预期上涨，DAX 指数创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/european-stocks-climb-as-rate-outlook-outweighs-tech-jitters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于西班牙通胀数据降温增强了人们对降息的预期，且保乐力加公司 (Pernod Ricard SA) 和 Delivery Hero SE 发布了稳健的盈利预测，欧洲股市上涨至七周高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/european-stocks-climb-as-rate-outlook-outweighs-tech-jitters</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 07:21:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国表示不会征收关税，人头马和保乐力加股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/pernod-says-us-china-sales-will-remain-soft-this-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国表示至少目前不会对欧盟白兰地征收临时关税后，人头马君度集团 (Remy Cointreau SA) 和保乐力加集团 (Pernod Ricard SA) 的股价飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/pernod-says-us-china-sales-will-remain-soft-this-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 05:27:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价在波动后维持跌势，焦点集中在中国和利比亚问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-29</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在连续两天下跌后企稳，因交易商担心利比亚供应中断将导致未来几个月油价走软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-29</guid>
